negative.review:
tldr; negative review because P2W

Objective facts;
You can purchase a battlepass which has DIRECT influences on your 'ability' to win a match in 2 ways; 
1) You get an extra hero choice. In this game, you don't get to choose your hero, instead you choose from 3 that is randomly selected and if you have the battle pass, you get an extra option. 
2) The above and other aspects of the game gets further exacerbated by 'tarot cards'. Tarot cards allow you to reroll MID-GAME, for heros and treasures(powerful relics that influence the match)

